article.description: — Sam Griesel posted 14 points as North Dakota State narrowly beat North Dakota 53-52 on Saturday.
article.headline: Griesel leads North Dakota St. over North Dakota 53-52
article.linkText: Griesel leads North Dakota St. over North Dakota 53-52
article.story: SIOUX FALLS, S.D. -- — Sam Griesel posted 14 points as North Dakota State narrowly beat North Dakota 53-52 on Saturday. Tyree Eady had 13 points for North Dakota State (2-5). Filip Rebraca had 21 points and seven rebounds for the Fighting Hawks (1-5). Seybian Sims added 5 points and 13 rebounds. Tyree Ihenacho had six assists. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
